title: Ep. - 541 - BACHELORETTE FINALE WITH GAME OF ROSES PODCAST REAL HOUSEWIVES OF BEVERLY HILLS THIS WEEK
description:
Kate discusses this week’s episode of Real Housewives of Beverly Hills.

 

Lizzy Pace and Chad Kultgen, co-hosts of Game of Roses, a podcast with in-depth coverage of the fastest growing professional sport in the world - The Bachelor. Lizzy and Chad are the foremost experts in gameplay analysis examining every episode as it airs as well as the history of the game and the plays that happen off the field in the parasocial arena of social media. It is the MoneyBall of The Bachelor. They are co-authors of How to Win the Bachelor: The Secret to Finding Love and Fame on America’s Favorite Reality Show.
